<font face="Karma Suture" size="54">{\an7}Help me to breathe</font>

17
00:02:09,910 --> 00:02:14,080
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I... I'm confused again.</font>

18
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:17,250
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Am I here? Or am I there?</font>

19
00:02:17,720 --> 00:02:21,520
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Over there, I'm everywhere. I know that.</font>

20
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:24,020
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I'm connected there, after all.</font>

21
00:02:24,530 --> 00:02:25,630
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Right?</font>

22
00:02:25,630 --> 00:02:28,600
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">But where is the real me?</font>

23
00:02:29,300 --> 00:02:32,830
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Oh, right. There is no real me.</font>

24
00:02:32,830 --> 00:02:36,640
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I only exist inside those people who are aware of my existence.</font>

25
00:02:36,640 --> 00:02:40,730
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">But this me that's talking right now...</font>

26
00:02:41,180 --> 00:02:42,730
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">It's me, isn't it?</font>

27
00:02:43,950 --> 00:02:48,590
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">This me that's talking... This me... Who is it?</font>

28
00:03:15,970 --> 00:03:17,100
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Arisu!</font>

29
00:03:25,780 --> 00:03:29,430
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">A body doesn't mean anything to you, right?</font>

30
00:03:38,060 --> 00:03:39,040
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Arisu...</font>

31
00:03:58,010 --> 00:03:59,310
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">No!</font>

32
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:14,240
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I mess up everything I try to do for you, huh, Arisu?</font>

33
00:04:14,660 --> 00:04:16,890
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Honest, I...</font>

34
00:04:27,840 --> 00:04:29,040
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Arisu!</font>

35
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:29,910
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Arisu!</font>

36
00:04:38,220 --> 00:04:39,620
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I'm sorry...</font>

37
00:04:40,320 --> 00:04:41,590
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I'm sorry...</font>

38
00:04:41,590 --> 00:04:44,710
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Arisu, I'm sorry...</font>

39
00:05:50,830 --> 00:05:51,910
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I'm done.</font>

40
00:05:52,330 --> 00:05:54,560
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Hey, you didn't clean your plate.</font>

41
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:58,250
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">She says she's on a diet.</font>

42
00:05:58,250 --> 00:06:00,930
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Tell the whole world, why don't you?</font>

43
00:06:06,540 --> 00:06:09,510
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Oh, I might get a package today. It's C.O.D.</font>

44
00:06:09,510 --> 00:06:11,210
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">If it comes, pay for it, okay?</font>

45
00:06:12,110 --> 00:06:14,430
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Computer parts again?</font>

46
00:06:26,060 --> 00:06:27,440
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Hey...</font>

47
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:29,230
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Yes?</font>

48
00:06:39,640 --> 00:06:41,800
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">No, it's nothing.</font>

49
00:07:52,710 --> 00:07:53,870
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Arisu!</font>

50
00:07:55,780 --> 00:07:59,420
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Arisu! We're going out tonight, right?</font>

51
00:07:59,420 --> 00:08:00,890
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Cyberia! Cyberia!</font>

52
00:08:00,890 --> 00:08:02,820
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Oh. Sure, why not?</font>

53
00:08:02,820 --> 00:08:04,260
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I'd better mail her, then.</font>

54
00:08:05,790 --> 00:08:09,320
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Arisu? Mail who?</font>

55
00:08:20,610 --> 00:08:24,140
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Oh, don't tell me you want her to come along again...</font>

56
00:08:25,950 --> 00:08:26,780
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">"Her"?</font>

57
00:08:34,820 --> 00:08:36,120
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Chisa?</font>

58
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:37,650
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Yeah. Yomoda Chisa.</font>

59
00:08:37,650 --> 00:08:40,620
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Arisu, you talked us into taking her to Cyberia once,</font>

60
00:08:41,830 --> 00:08:45,430
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">but it's like she just didn't care.</font>

61
00:08:45,430 --> 00:08:47,200
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Inviting her is pointless.</font>

62
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:48,650
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Oh, I get it...</font>

63
00:08:49,130 --> 00:08:49,670
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Huh?</font>

64
00:08:52,510 --> 00:08:54,180
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">It's nothing.</font>

65
00:08:54,180 --> 00:08:55,670
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I just thought of something strange.</font>

66
00:08:56,040 --> 00:08:58,110
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Something strange?</font>

67
00:08:58,110 --> 00:09:01,120
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">If you don't remember something, it never happened.</font>

68
00:09:01,120 --> 00:09:02,320
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Don't remember?</font>

69
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:05,680
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">If you aren't remembered, you never existed.</font>

70
00:09:08,520 --> 00:09:09,250
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Who are you talking about?</font>

71
00:09:09,250 --> 00:09:11,190
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Who are you talking about?</font>

72
00:09:12,130 --> 00:09:15,830
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Like I said. Nobody.</font>

73
00:09:15,830 --> 00:09:18,300
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Come on, we'd better hit the books.</font>

74
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:20,260
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Arisu!</font>

75
00:09:32,020 --> 00:09:32,870
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Go!</font>

76
00:09:34,120 --> 00:09:37,460
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Man, I gotta do it again?</font>

77
00:09:37,460 --> 00:09:39,150
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Come on, one more time!</font>

78
00:09:39,150 --> 00:09:40,390
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Hurry up!</font>

79
00:09:40,390 --> 00:09:41,980
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Wait for me!</font>

80
00:09:42,520 --> 00:09:45,220
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">You're such a sucker!</font>

81
00:09:48,130 --> 00:09:49,330
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Mail?</font>

82
00:09:49,330 --> 00:09:50,480
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">What is it?</font>

83
00:09:55,640 --> 00:09:57,590
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Who's that girl?!</font>

84
00:09:57,590 --> 00:10:00,540
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I don't know.</font>

85
00:10:00,540 --> 00:10:01,910
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Now what?</font>

86
00:10:01,910 --> 00:10:03,490
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Hey, nice machine!</font>

87
00:10:05,850 --> 00:10:08,320
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Mine's pretty tricked out, too.</font>

88
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:10,850
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Come on! Hurry!</font>

89
00:10:12,190 --> 00:10:14,180
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Come on! Come on!</font>

90
00:10:14,180 --> 00:10:16,250
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Mom's waiting!</font>

91
00:10:16,890 --> 00:10:19,120
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Okay, okay... Bye.</font>

92
00:10:21,930 --> 00:10:23,060
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Let's go!</font>

93
00:10:23,060 --> 00:10:25,600
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Wait! Shoot for it again!</font>

94
00:10:28,220 --> 00:10:30,170
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Hurry up, Taro!</font>

95
00:10:30,170 --> 00:10:32,400
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">No fair! Shoot for it again!</font>

96
00:10:36,340 --> 00:10:39,940
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I'll quit. I'll quit that dump.</font>

97
00:10:40,520 --> 00:10:42,450
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">The crap they make me do...</font>

98
00:10:43,220 --> 00:10:45,210
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">They all underestimate me...</font>

99
00:10:46,490 --> 00:10:48,390
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Oh, well.</font>

100
00:10:49,960 --> 00:10:51,930
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I'm gonna quit... I'm gonna quit!</font>

101
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:17,890
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I'm gonna quit!</font>

102
00:11:17,890 --> 00:11:19,480
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I'm gonna quit today for sure!</font>

103
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:46,030
What isn't remembered never happened

104
00:11:46,030 --> 00:11:50,830
Memory is merely a record

105
00:11:52,870 --> 00:12:05,300
You just need to rewrite that record

106
00:12:02,400 --> 00:12:03,460
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Is that true?</font>

107
00:12:09,240 --> 00:12:12,580
<font face="Bembo Std Semibold" size="54" color="#c21411">Present Day</font>

108
00:12:12,340 --> 00:12:15,440
<font face="Bembo Std Semibold" size="54" color="#c21411">Present Time</font>

109
00:13:13,800 --> 00:13:15,670
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Why are you crying?</font>

110
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:20,190
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Because you deleted yourself from everyone's memory?</font>

111
00:13:24,380 --> 00:13:27,610
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">But isn't that what you wanted?</font>

112
00:13:29,150 --> 00:13:31,450
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Yes, but...</font>

113
00:13:31,450 --> 00:13:36,780
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">No one is dying, and no one is being hurt.</font>

114
00:13:37,790 --> 00:13:40,210
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">And no one hates you.</font>

115
00:13:41,100 --> 00:13:43,210
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Yes, but...</font>

116
00:13:44,100 --> 00:13:50,220
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Dead people's information isn't leaking out of the Wired anymore.</font>

117
00:13:55,780 --> 00:13:59,800
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">So Lain doesn't need to be anywhere anymore.</font>

118
00:14:00,690 --> 00:14:03,270
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">This is what you wanted, isn't it?</font>

119
00:14:04,720 --> 00:14:07,580
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">You sound just like him.</font>

120
00:14:07,580 --> 00:14:09,220
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Him?</font>

121
00:14:09,220 --> 00:14:11,630
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">That man never existed now.</font>

122
00:14:11,630 --> 00:14:15,530
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Even if he does, he won't get any ideas into his head about being God.</font>

123
00:14:16,060 --> 00:14:18,730
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I'm nowhere now...</font>

124
00:14:18,730 --> 00:14:22,530
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">If I'm nowhere, who am I?</font>

125
00:14:22,530 --> 00:14:25,110
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Where am I?</font>

126
00:14:25,110 --> 00:14:26,770
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">You yourself said it.</font>

127
00:14:27,510 --> 00:14:31,310
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">The Wired isn't an upper layer of the real world.</font>

128
00:14:31,310 --> 00:14:34,070
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">That's what that man was mistaken about.</font>

129
00:14:35,150 --> 00:14:37,850
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">A network is a field to pass along information.</font>

130
00:14:39,150 --> 00:14:41,620
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Information doesn't stand still there.</font>

131
00:14:41,620 --> 00:14:44,770
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Information functions by always being in motion.</font>

132
00:14:46,360 --> 00:14:47,770
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Really?</font>

133
00:14:48,040 --> 00:14:54,820
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">People's memories aren't just personal or one part of the history of humanity.</font>

134
00:14:56,740 --> 00:15:00,290
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">No, not even the shared unconscious.</font>

135
00:15:00,290 --> 00:15:04,210
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Do you think that humans could create something that could store</font>

136
00:15:04,210 --> 00:15:07,140
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">memory that's that vast?</font>

137
00:15:08,750 --> 00:15:11,780
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">The Wired was just connected to something else...</font>

138
00:15:12,290 --> 00:15:15,650
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">But where was it connected to?</font>

139
00:15:20,460 --> 00:15:23,760
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Do people really need to know that?</font>

140
00:15:25,990 --> 00:15:30,060
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Look at how far they've come without knowing.</font>

141
00:15:31,670 --> 00:15:35,610
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">The human world creates and prays to its various gods,</font>

142
00:15:35,610 --> 00:15:38,210
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">and humans convince themselves, "This is how the world is."</font>

143
00:15:42,880 --> 00:15:44,830
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I don't like how you're saying this.</font>

144
00:15:45,890 --> 00:15:49,350
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Either way, it's Lain that's saying it. Me.</font>

145
00:15:49,350 --> 00:15:50,840
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">You understand that, right?</font>

146
00:15:53,230 --> 00:15:56,920
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Oh, right... Lain was never a person, was she?</font>

147
00:16:02,900 --> 00:16:06,430
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Lain is omnipresent, existing everywhere.</font>

148
00:16:06,430 --> 00:16:08,860
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Lain watches quietly.</font>

149
00:16:09,680 --> 00:16:12,340
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Right, Lain is God!</font>

150
00:16:12,980 --> 00:16:14,000
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">No...</font>

151
00:16:15,380 --> 00:16:16,970
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">You're wrong!</font>

152
00:16:18,420 --> 00:16:21,240
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">It'd be so much easier if you became God.</font>

153
00:16:21,660 --> 00:16:24,500
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I think it'd be a lot easier than being a human.</font>

154
00:16:28,260 --> 00:16:32,310
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">You wouldn't have to do anything. Just stand there and watch.</font>

155
00:16:32,310 --> 00:16:35,030
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">No one would look down on Lain.</font>

156
00:16:35,430 --> 00:16:37,900
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">No one would hate Lain.</font>

157
00:16:38,540 --> 00:16:40,060
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">That's...</font>

158
00:16:45,280 --> 00:16:51,840
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Hey, Lain, let's start everything over again from the beginning!</font>

159
00:16:52,250 --> 00:16:54,950
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I mean, you did go and reset everything, after all...</font>

160
00:16:55,650 --> 00:16:57,090
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Stop it!</font>

161
00:17:25,850 --> 00:17:28,910
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Then what are you, Lain?</font>

162
00:17:31,590 --> 00:17:32,700
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I...</font>

163
00:17:33,090 --> 00:17:34,670
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I...</font>

164
00:17:36,100 --> 00:17:38,630
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Where am I?</font>

165
00:17:39,570 --> 00:17:41,090
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Come, Lain.</font>

166
00:18:01,860 --> 00:18:03,350
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Dad?</font>

167
00:18:17,090 --> 00:18:21,450
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">You don't need to wear that anymore, Lain.</font>

168
00:18:27,950 --> 00:18:30,720
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Dad, do you know?</font>

169
00:18:30,720 --> 00:18:32,080
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">What?</font>

170
00:18:32,550 --> 00:18:35,880
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I... Everyone, I...</font>

171
00:18:36,220 --> 00:18:37,990
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">You love them?</font>

172
00:18:41,100 --> 00:18:42,730
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Isn't that right?</font>

173
00:18:49,200 --> 00:18:52,830
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Lain, I'll make us some nice tea next time.</font>

174
00:18:54,180 --> 00:18:58,630
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Hey, with some madeleines! Definitely. They're great!</font>

175
00:19:09,590 --> 00:19:13,030
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">So memories aren't only of the past, are they?</font>

176
00:19:14,560 --> 00:19:18,180
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">They can be of right now, or even of tomorrow.</font>

177
00:19:25,510 --> 00:19:26,470
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Unbelievable!</font>

178
00:19:26,470 --> 00:19:28,530
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Isn't it? But hang on a second...</font>

179
00:19:28,530 --> 00:19:32,640
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I listened to what you had to say.</font>

180
00:19:33,110 --> 00:19:35,140
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Very patiently, I might add.</font>

181
00:19:35,880 --> 00:19:38,720
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I get to pick the curtains for the bedroom, right?</font>

182
00:19:38,720 --> 00:19:40,080
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Yes, ma'am.</font>

183
00:19:42,660 --> 00:19:44,990
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Anything you say.</font>

184
00:19:44,990 --> 00:19:47,040
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">All right, then. That's a good student.</font>

185
00:19:50,530 --> 00:19:51,390
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Something wrong?</font>

186
00:19:51,390 --> 00:19:52,830
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">No.</font>

187
00:20:03,080 --> 00:20:05,170
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Sorry, could you wait here a minute?</font>

188
00:20:05,170 --> 00:20:06,710
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Hey, what're you...</font>

189
00:20:28,400 --> 00:20:29,700
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Hello.</font>

190
00:20:30,470 --> 00:20:31,830
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Hello.</font>

191
00:20:32,970 --> 00:20:35,830
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Have we met before? We have, haven't we?</font>

192
00:20:40,210 --> 00:20:42,810
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Did you go to the school I was a student teacher at?</font>

193
00:20:43,220 --> 00:20:45,620
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">No, that can't be it...</font>

194
00:20:45,620 --> 00:20:46,840
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Let me think...</font>

195
00:20:48,390 --> 00:20:49,840
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Pleased to meet you.</font>

196
00:20:50,460 --> 00:20:51,450
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Huh?</font>

197
00:20:52,290 --> 00:20:54,690
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Pleased to meet you. We haven't met before.</font>

198
00:20:55,730 --> 00:20:58,490
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Oh. Well, I'm pleased to meet you, then.</font>

199
00:20:58,490 --> 00:21:00,270
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I'm Arisu.</font>

200
00:21:01,200 --> 00:21:04,870
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Strange name, huh? I'm kind of embarrassed about it.</font>

201
00:21:06,140 --> 00:21:07,400
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">What's yours?</font>

202
00:21:08,480 --> 00:21:09,570
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Lain.</font>

203
00:21:10,950 --> 00:21:12,470
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Lain?</font>

204
00:21:14,650 --> 00:21:15,610
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">A friend of yours?</font>

205
00:21:15,610 --> 00:21:17,810
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">No, I thought she was someone else.</font>

206
00:21:19,390 --> 00:21:21,480
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Well, goodbye, Lain.</font>

207
00:21:21,480 --> 00:21:24,590
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Maybe we'll run into each other again someday.</font>

208
00:21:28,400 --> 00:21:29,360
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Bye.</font>

209
00:21:29,360 --> 00:21:30,830
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Bye, Lain.</font>

210
00:21:43,110 --> 00:21:46,270
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">You're right. We can see each other anytime.</font>

211
00:22:06,300 --> 00:22:10,630
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I'm here, so I'll be with you forever.</font>

212
00:22:40,750 --> 00:22:45,180
<font face="Bembo Std Semibold" size="35">{\an8}nan no tsumi mo nai hazu na no ni</font>

213
00:22:40,750 --> 00:22:45,180
<font face="Bembo Std Semibold" size="35">Although I must be innocent,</font>

214
00:22:45,180 --> 00:22:49,090
<font face="Bembo Std Semibold" size="35">{\an8}nanraka no batsu wo uketeru</font>

215
00:22:45,180 --> 00:22:49,090
<font face="Bembo Std Semibold" size="35">now I am punished.</font>

216
00:22:49,520 --> 00:22:55,390
<font face="Bembo Std Semibold" size="35">{\an8}jibun de maita tane de mo nai no ni</font>

217
00:22:49,520 --> 00:22:55,390
<font face="Bembo Std Semibold" size="35">I wasn't the one who sowed those seeds, but nevertheless</font>

218
00:22:56,110 --> 00:23:02,300
<font face="Bembo Std Semibold" size="35">{\an8}sakimidareta hana tsumasareru</font>

219
00:22:56,110 --> 00:23:02,300
<font face="Bembo Std Semibold" size="35">I have to pull up the flowers that bloomed from them.</font>

220
00:23:08,850 --> 00:23:13,490
<font face="Bembo Std Semibold" size="35">{\an8}shiranai koto to mo ienai ga</font>

221
00:23:08,850 --> 00:23:13,490
<font face="Bembo Std Semibold" size="35">I can't say I didn't know about it,</font>

222
00:23:13,490 --> 00:23:17,940
<font face="Bembo Std Semibold" size="35">{\an8}katabou katsuida oboe wa nai</font>

223
00:23:13,490 --> 00:23:17,940
<font face="Bembo Std Semibold" size="35">but I don't remember taking any part in it.</font>

224
00:23:17,940 --> 00:23:24,130
<font face="Bembo Std Semibold" size="35">{\an8}jiyuu wo takaku kawasareta ki mo suru ga</font>

225
00:23:17,940 --> 00:23:24,130
<font face="Bembo Std Semibold" size="35">I think my freedom cost me dearly,</font>

226
00:23:24,660 --> 00:23:31,370
<font face="Bembo Std Semibold" size="35">{\an8}kokoro made yasuku utta oboe wa nai</font>

227
00:23:24,660 --> 00:23:31,370
<font face="Bembo Std Semibold" size="35">but I don't remember selling my soul so cheaply.</font>

228
00:23:31,730 --> 00:23:39,420
<font face="Bembo Std Semibold" size="35">{\an8}Hey Hey kutabatte osaraba suru made</font>

229
00:23:31,730 --> 00:23:39,420
<font face="Bembo Std Semibold" size="35">Hey hey, until I die and say farewell...</font>

230
00:23:40,440 --> 00:23:49,330
<font face="Bembo Std Semibold" size="35">{\an8}Hey Hey dare no te ni mo kakaranai</font>

231
00:23:40,440 --> 00:23:49,330
<font face="Bembo Std Semibold" size="35">Hey hey... no one can touch me.</font>

232
00:23:50,850 --> 00:23:54,940
<font face="Bembo Std Semibold" size="35">{\an8}tooi yoru wo urotsuiteiru</font>

233
00:23:50,850 --> 00:23:54,940
<font face="Bembo Std Semibold" size="35">You probably don't know</font>

234
00:23:54,940 --> 00:24:02,650
<font face="Bembo Std Semibold" size="35">{\an8}shiranai darou eien no narazu monotachi wo</font>

235
00:23:54,940 --> 00:24:02,650
<font face="Bembo Std Semibold" size="35">the eternal outlaws prowling in the distant night.</font>

